description:
What is spiritual warfare? Walter and Sonica Veith have experienced spiritual warfare firsthand and talk about their encounters. Walter Veith and his wife Sonica review their growing up years and early adulthood. Hear about the paranormal phenomena that plagued them in their early married life and different methods of exorcism they tried. Find out what they learned about how to get rid of ghosts and evil spirits.

Hear the amazing story of God’s miraculous interventions as He walked the Veiths out of darkness into His glorious light.

For more lectures please visit:
http://amazingdiscoveries.tv/c/22/Walter_Veith/

Visit our website: http://amazingdiscoveries.org
